<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw kalvari tang khu ka vak thil a,
 Ka hukdampa thihna tang chu;
 Mi tizat tang, tang thavaih um a chun,
 Ka thuok sikin A thuok.

[V2]
 Ka kipak ie Lalpa, ka kipak ie,
 Zie bang lawma hehpihna mak;
 Ka genthiem puoi na phatna zozai hi,
 Hun pak chim thei puo'ng ka.

[V3]
 2. Zie bang lawm lawma hehpihna mak hi,
 Suol tuipi a tummang sa nung;.
 Na hehpih na'n nei hung puidawk ta a,
 Nang chauh hun zui tang ka.

[V4]
 3. Na thisan in na hawng zalenna gam,
 Zie mun chuh ei puitung ding in;
 Na Thagau a nei hung panpih ziekin,
 Ka lung a awi ngei ie,

[V5]
 4. Gen chim thei hiel puo'ng ka, na hehpihna,
 Khawvel lopina genlo in;
 Na hehpihna thu mai hi gen tang ka.
 Lalpa ei panpih in.

[V6]
 5. Hallelujah amen, Halleluijah.
 Amen....Amen Halleluijah;
 Lalpa vangsakna tincheng eipie pa
 Na min lopi zing hen.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Kipak Ngei Ie Lalpa</title>
<hymn_number>292</hymn_number>
</song>